      <p class="calibre19">“You may be right. I don’t care. As any car freak will tell you, the old models are the most beautiful, even if they aren’t the most efficient. People who sacrifice beauty for efficiency get what they deserve.”</p>
      <p class="calibre19">“Well, you may get off on being a beautiful stereotype, regardless of the social consequences, but my conscience won’t allow it. And I goddamn <span class="italic">refuse</span> to be dragon bait. I’m as capable of rescuing you as you are of rescuing me.”</p>
